{"tid":2161320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民聽住：你地一接受委任，就唔再係民選議員","createTime":"2020-08-17T13:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:53:36.000Z","uid":154486,"like":88,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3354b1acace59bfea616c1d7c3d4859121e286cb","tid":2161320,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"香港人2016選你係做四年<br />\n本土派比尊重你地<br />\n唔係因為你地係泛民，係你地背後既2016年既民意基礎<br />\n<br />\n你一接受人大委任<br />\n請唔好再自稱自己為民選議員<br />\n亦都請停止自稱<strong>「泛民主派」</strong><br />\n學返中共講法，你地只係<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>反對派</strong></span><br />\n你地就係人大入面果1票反對<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3zrFRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3zrFRJ.jpg&h=d2e807c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><p class=\"center\">請好好做個忠誠既反對派，你地唔可以自稱為民選泛民議員<br />\n</p></span></span>"},{"pid":"12660103e404b3835cffaa8d90e9e0f725722aec","tid":2161320,"uid":136431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"違憲任命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5998cea025e6c68dbe4e70723466cc19181aca91","tid":2161320,"uid":154486,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">受委任一年 = 民意歸零</span></strong><br />\n我地將唔會當你係民意代表，無資格為香港人做任何決定"},{"pid":"d2d2a715fdc8765f7e9118d0d2a5e3b4881773c7","tid":2161320,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5f759d3a603c84f5f0da21ee468269fb98b7d57","tid":2161320,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a